{"tid":1681183,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"前線巴，好似鐘意咗個女同事，去唔去好。。。","createTime":"2019-10-29T09:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T07:58:48.000Z","uid":330025,"like":37,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"eccff96efa5c40f365069955dd716c0b47b550f2","tid":1681183,"uid":330025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:04:31.000Z","msg":"有啲內容要登入至睇到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n背景<br />\nA0 就20歲，學生一個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有少少摺 仲要本身並唔仲意同人講野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大我3年<br />\n追星族嚟，成日飛 ( 我唔介意佢追星，亦冇打算干涉)<br />\n<br />\n我本身打機算係超勁，佢亦都鐘意打機<br />\n因為鐘意既game唔同，未一齊打過<br />\n佢亦都表明過鐘意睇人打機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大概咁概<br />\n<br />\n2/3月已經開始free到我對佢有少少好感<br />\n6月交換咗ig <br />\n開始叫做不時有ig&amp;wts 傾下計<br />\n有時成幾日都有傾，有時成個禮拜都冇msg過咁濟。。。<br />\n佢本身有時好夜訓，有時會msg到好撚夜<br />\n<br />\n咁都放工之後有出過黎食吓宵夜咁既<br />\n最近食完有一齊行去巴士站<br />\n一邊陪佢等通宵車，一邊傾計<br />\n<br />\n有時傾吓自己屋企，食既野，打機，1啲芝麻小事，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw,<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一嚟，<br />\n我feel到佢對我唔係討厭<br />\n但佢本身都算係對人熱情既<br />\n又係追星族<br />\n佢對我有冇好感我都唔敢肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2嚟，<br />\n我真係好撚矛盾<br />\n我怕自己如果有個萬一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知仲有冇機會可以講到<br />\n但我亦都好怕只係我自己自作多情，get 錯野<br />\n<br />\nsome for 1999，<br />\n求各位巴絲俾啲意見，etc點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟A0仔,真係冇乜經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋如果建議去，就正皮<br />\n唔建議去，就負皮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc734da62d1836cd1703f01fcf7f6d268349456d","tid":1681183,"uid":214635,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:05:39.000Z","msg":"中出即飛"},{"pid":"2372f05c452251e8116e3854fcbf45dc223bf232","tid":1681183,"uid":175168,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"聽過一句好真實既說話<br />\n<br />\n溝咩女都好...一定唔好溝同事"},{"pid":"f022aab4af0706c1353e1b87bc5cfc57baa182e5","tid":1681183,"uid":68598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:06:48.000Z","msg":"順其啦 <br />\n反而果2位手足點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bb883856fdf68074976087cd352a4046ee5039","tid":1681183,"uid":136893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:06:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"904a7c041e24487e43c2e829ff1701e28d225f58","tid":1681183,"uid":71657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:07:19.000Z","msg":"放棄啦溝同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30cbaa87607093b87a0b4a9cc9ded4427aff180","tid":1681183,"uid":330025,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f022aab4af0706c1353e1b87bc5cfc57baa182e5","tid":1681183,"uid":68598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:06:48.000Z","msg":"順其啦 <br />