},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"見過太多。好多唔聽勸。跟住奶野<br />\n當然有成功例子。<br />\n<br />\n除非你自問好成熟。好多野識放得低<br />\n或者大家都係適婚年齡，或者有人諗住轉工"},{"pid":"293a84f83e2c9b38bead5548bd37823a390206ae","tid":1681183,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:21:02.000Z","msg":"打機咁叻想去馬就去馬<br />\ng持"},{"pid":"f7c682e68bda8d210ff42f1bb867ec528355fdc4","tid":1681183,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9df280cb1fa0d8e1186f3f16bd8684459e05c622","tid":1681183,"uid":330025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51a7bd2ee9f14d971654cc52c96b14eefa5cbc61","tid":1681183,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T11:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:03:01.000Z","msg":"冇經驗<br />\n所以求指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:27:10.000Z","msg":"多啲約下佢？"},{"pid":"683632d78bbe25a509e97c48f9e90a87b6bd5bdc","tid":1681183,"uid":316810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60cb1330ab1514eb33216db33ab3fa6a1b7eaca7","tid":1681183,"uid":330025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8912fa0544bbf9c9d411de159efa36c173891ba","tid":1681183,"uid":316810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eccff96efa5c40f365069955dd716c0b47b550f2","tid":1681183,"uid":330025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:04:31.000Z","msg":"有啲內容要登入至睇到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n背景<br />\nA0 就20歲，學生一個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有少少摺 仲要本身並唔仲意同人講野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大我3年<br />\n追星族嚟，成日飛 ( 我唔介意佢追星，亦冇打算干涉)<br />\n<br />\n我本身打機算係超勁，佢亦都鐘意打機<br />\n因為鐘意既game唔同，未一齊打過<br />\n佢亦都表明過鐘意睇人打機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大概咁概<br />\n<br />\n2/3月已經開始free到我對佢有少少好感<br />\n6月交換咗ig <br />\n開始叫做不時有ig&amp;wts 傾下計<br />\n有時成幾日都有傾，有時成個禮拜都冇msg過咁濟。。。<br />\n佢本身有時好夜訓，有時會msg到好撚夜<br />\n<br />\n咁都放工之後有出過黎食吓宵夜咁既<br />\n最近食完有一齊行去巴士站<br />\n一邊陪佢等通宵車，一邊傾計<br />\n<br />\n有時傾吓自己屋企，食既野，打機，1啲芝麻小事，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw,<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一嚟，<br />\n我feel到佢對我唔係討厭<br />\n但佢本身都算係對人熱情既<br />\n又係追星族<br />\n佢對我有冇好感我都唔敢肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2嚟，<br />\n我真係好撚矛盾<br />\n我怕自己如果有個萬一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知仲有冇機會可以講到<br />\n但我亦都好怕只係我自己自作多情，get 錯野<br />\n<br />\nsome for 1999，<br />\n求各位巴絲俾啲意見，etc點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟A0仔,真係冇乜經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋如果建議去，就正皮<br />\n唔建議去，就負皮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:28:50.000Z","msg":"唔好錯過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:08:03.000Z","msg":"如果真係啱嘅，我都唔想錯過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:27:39.000Z","msg":"鼓起勇氣 錯過左 只會後悔一世 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油 成功左 話我知"},{"pid":"52ac2a02cbfc92e54f77bdfbd9c5946c894f61de","tid":1681183,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"勇武反而唔識溝女<img src=\"/assets/fa